{"tid":1913602,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔需要理會PK Tang呻淫: 警隊創新低 40%市民給0分","createTime":"2020-03-07T02:44:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-09T10:21:48.000Z","uid":123774,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d32000608ef9b9a9cfa77d6e9c1129de01b4a652","tid":1913602,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T02:44:33.000Z","msg":"鄧柄強先生<br />\n香港人睇你地係三萬古惑仔 社會寄生蟲<br />\n&ldquo;你地長命百歲 家人橫屍街頭&rdquo;係香港人共識<br />\n民意從來都唔嚮你地個邊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【香港民研】紀律部隊評分下跌　警隊創新低　四成市民給零分<br />\n最後更新日期：2019-12-06 18:08<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港民意研究所今日（6日）公布紀律部隊及駐港解放軍民望數字，市民對紀律部隊的滿意度，排名首位的是消防處，其次是醫療輔助隊、政府飛行服務隊、海關和入境處等，其中警務處的評分，在9個紀律部隊中排名最低，當中有4成市民給予零分，連同駐港解放軍的滿意淨值，相關題目的評分都是自1997年開展以來最低。<br />\n<br />\n反修訂《逃犯條例》風波持續，警民衝突不時發生，其中警察疑執法不公的問題甚為社會關注。<br />\n<br />\n僅35.3分　滿意淨值為負38個百分點<br />\n<br />\n香港民研在11月底訪問1,062名市民，結果發現市民對紀律部隊的<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>滿意度排名第一至二位是消防處和醫療輔助隊，評分分別為80.5分及80.2分。位列第三至第八位的是政府飛行服務隊、海關、入境事務處、民安隊、懲教署和廉政公署。警務處的評分最低，只有35.3分，當中有40%市民給予零分，滿意率為27%，不滿率為65%，滿意淨值為負38個百分點。</strong></span></span> <br />\n<br />\n較6月調查重挫25.7個百分點<br />\n<br />\n與6月時的調查結果比較，除了醫療輔助隊外，其餘8個紀律部隊的滿意評分都有所下跌，當中警務處的跌幅尤其顯著，下跌了25.7個百分點，其次是廉政公署和政府飛行服務隊，分別下跌了9.8個百分點和8.5個百分點。"},{"pid":"8d282cc118657519f06b91006e613b30df5b7035","tid":1913602,"uid":26876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T02:48:36.000Z","msg":"曱甴強鳩Up無數據同證據"},{"pid":"b014a5c13e15e1d47ed0bf439e12be6de8af7806","tid":1913602,"uid":54653,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T02:52:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/irU0rM4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FirU0rM4.jpg&h=fdc9870c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bf05f905ffb18c89dbb869653a186d27481431ab","tid":1913602,"uid":26876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T02:53:31.000Z","msg":"曱甴強鳩噏不敢面對的數據"},{"pid":"32391389ddf7cf7822a7e6200989e165537d44f0","tid":1913602,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T03:10:03.000Z","msg":"警隊想永續ot"},{"pid":"522ed1e373b0ec9c2cf9f53da9af902a3eb0655e","tid":1913602,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T03:20:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78727ea46fa84fac8a1bf088e2fbe4bb20bfc11d","tid":1913602,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T03:21:23.000Z","msg":"消防都趺好多喎<br />\n上次好似係90%以上?"},{"pid":"51c2eb1f83b251b70c3a57e8ba7a87d5aa91357a","tid":1913602,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T03:29:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d0c72ed7f5c801be4c232316afe8e12be6d25f5","tid":1913602,"uid":45498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T03:30:57.000Z","msg":"咁少人俾零分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"220428fe17a806ec04ba18902415fc1eb733f0a5","tid":1913602,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T05:36:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"946a3459218c742b5d9663d5c02bd1436e4b3276","tid":1913602,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T08:04:54.000Z","msg":"鄧柄強 你死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38540b1630dc17ef41fcc18d8d34f402b4f5c698","tid":1913602,"uid":140737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T08:16:23.000Z","msg":"曱甴強我屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f21d0b340b7ee1076